replies.body: I appreciate the updated client being proactive, but I don't believe those issues would cause your patcher to corrupt.  Hopefully that restart fixes it up, but I recommend using our[ patcher report guide ](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/230673527)to let our client devs know about this.  Thanks for the report!
Done, also if anyone else is having this issue I uninstalled then reinstalled without accepting the new client and am just playing on the old one.
